<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <title>CashLift — See the impact of your donation</title>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="landing">
    <section class="hero">
      <span class="eyebrow">Every dollar, accounted for</span>
      <h1>Know exactly what your donation does.</h1>
      <p>
        CashLift uses AI to translate any donation amount into a clear,
        real-world picture of the impact it can have against global poverty.
        No vague promises — just a clear explanation, every time you give.
      </p>
      <% if (!user) { %>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-primary">Go to Dashboard</a>
      <% } %>
    </section>

    <div class="sample-receipt">
      <p class="receipt-label">Sample receipt</p>
      <div class="receipt-row">
        <span>Clean Water</span>
        <span class="receipt-amount">$25</span>
      </div>
      <div class="perforation"></div>
      <p class="receipt-impact">
        "A $25 donation could provide a family with safe drinking water
        for about a month — this is the kind of explanation you'll get
        for every donation you log."
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <p>&copy; 2026 CashLift. A student project.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>